---
title: Plant-Based Pumpkin Ravioli & Creamy Bacon-Spinach Sauce with Baby Broccoli
description: Let’s have some fun with this plant-based ravioli packed full of pumpkin and coated in a creamy bacon sauce seasoned with herbs and spinach. Add a zap of chilli flakes to zest up the baby broccoli and finish with a punch of flavour.
